          <groundspeak:finder id="931570">22wander</groundspeak:finder>
          <groundspeak:text encoded="False">Deleting our "Will attend".   Have need to get home turf sooner than we originally thought.  Sorry to miss this event but will (hopefully) see you on Sunday in Sioux Falls.</groundspeak:text>
        </groundspeak:log>
