  <wpt lat="41.249617" lon="-96.082667">
    <time>2026-05-20T11:15:00</time>
    <name>GCBP29X</name>
    <desc>Omaha Lunch #83 by TeamDAAK, Event Cache (1.0/1.0)</desc>
    <url>https://coord.info/GCBP29X</url>
    <urlname>Omaha Lunch #83</urlname>
    <sym>Geocache</sym>
    <type>Geocache|Event Cache</type>
    <groundspeak:cache id="10405242" archived="False" available="False" xmlns:groundspeak="http://www.groundspeak.com/cache/1/0/1">
      <groundspeak:name>Omaha Lunch #83</groundspeak:name>
      <groundspeak:placed_by>TeamDAAK</groundspeak:placed_by>
      <groundspeak:owner id="3878551">TeamDAAK</groundspeak:owner>
      <groundspeak:type>Event Cache</groundspeak:type>
      <groundspeak:container>Other</groundspeak:container>
      <groundspeak:attributes>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="24" inc="1">Wheelchair accessible</groundspeak:attribute>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="6" inc="1">Recommended for kids</groundspeak:attribute>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="41" inc="1">Stroller accessible</groundspeak:attribute>
        <groundspeak:attribute id="25" inc="1">Parking nearby</groundspeak:attribute>
      </groundspeak:attributes>
      <groundspeak:difficulty>1.0</groundspeak:difficulty>
      <groundspeak:terrain>1.0</groundspeak:terrain>
      <groundspeak:country>United States</groundspeak:country>
      <groundspeak:state>Nebraska</groundspeak:state>
      <groundspeak:short_description html="True">&lt;b&gt;20 May 2026, 11:15 - 12:15&lt;/b&gt;</groundspeak:short_description>
      <groundspeak:long_description html="True">&lt;p&gt;Welcome to this monthly geocaching event series, which will hopefully take you to different locations each month for lunch in the greater Omaha area.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;When:&lt;/strong&gt;Wednesday, May 20th at 11:15 am - 12:15 pm&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Where:&lt;/strong&gt;Clean Eatz&lt;br /&gt;
920 S 107th Ave Suite 110&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha, NE 68114&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;As always, no purchase is necessary just come by to visit and have a good time. Please, no outside food or drink.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Event ownership is open to everyone, and the event owner decides on the date, time, and location,&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;preferably someplace new to the event&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; (see the long list of places already used below). If you would like to be the event owner for an upcoming month, please attend this current event or coordinate with the current event owner before the next event.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This monthly lunch has been going on since January 21, 2019, even through COVID-19!!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Past Omaha Lunch Events&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Omaha Lunch #001 at Don &amp;amp; Millies hosted by TeamDAAK&lt;br /&gt;
Omaha Lunch #002 at The Corner Kick - Street Tacos and Sports Cantina hosted by jenny08_1015&lt;br /&gt;
