          <groundspeak:finder id="2043214">WadeLori</groundspeak:finder>
          <groundspeak:text encoded="False">Great day for Geocaching, almost any day is good for that.
I love it when we get free time to go outside and play.

Stopping in before work. Then of course the long way back to Omaha. Glad I only ate one donut...weeeee. thanks for hosting and setting up the ALC   NE. 
All is well here. 
TFTC

